T1  - Relational Contracts, Multiple Agents, and Correlated Outputs
AU  - Kvaløy, Ola
AU  - Olsen, Trond E.
Y1  - 2019/05/14
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2018.3162
